Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我这么说了就发射吧  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊！？
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着把头发绑起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  稍稍有点姐姐的感觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:49.73,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N42
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  博士有多像姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  非常像姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么名乃呢  名乃有多像？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我恐怕没有那么像姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得妙  是的  恐怕是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  既然没办法  就让博士来收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾呀收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我还在看这本书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  阪本也让人操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然这样  你有什么阴谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本你真是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说你要帮我盖的话就用毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  阪本  你这是强词夺理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士我来洗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要把定时器转一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由博士来转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  真的只要转一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了博士我要转啦  让博士来转啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困难请找博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿名乃没办法  就由博士来做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我现在已经在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士做的更好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你看  住手啦  很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:30.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}博士我会做的  没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让我来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可看不出有什么没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烫死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫死了  烫死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你…你没事吧  阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都做了什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿阪本你没办法啊  在这种地方走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法你个头啦  还不都是你们瞎搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  阪本  生气也解决不了什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你在讲什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之再重新煎个蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么就由博士来煎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其他的菜会冷掉的  所以要快点煎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  名乃啊  博士都说了我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士  很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋会掉下去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姑娘  今天这个小鬼是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想做姐姐感觉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是姐姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐可是不吃零食的  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵  变回平时的博士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蒙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.48,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(600,0)}河\N边\N垂\N钓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看来是条大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是长筒靴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这次才是真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上这不是比鱼还要厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会有这么有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该邀请别人一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}桃太郎…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒手寿司
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:26.08,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N43
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底为什么我非得做作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  虽然说我确实成绩不好  不做不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是具备设法回避不及格的能力的  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升学没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不想毕业了再到大学去继续读书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就业？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前在电视上看到就业难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有学历的话很难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就职
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法避免的大学入学考试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是不想学习！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底现在进行的学习对将来有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来的梦想是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来的梦想  相生祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来的梦想是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成伞蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞蜥  伞蜥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想学习！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想学习也不想变成伞蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说要是变成伞蜥蜴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会摆脱这个烦恼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果反正要变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆变成国宝大师受到追捧也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:56.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}粘土般的某物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说国宝大师每月能赚多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要怎样才能变成国宝大师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根结底  国宝大师是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  还是更加现实地考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了啊  完全找不到方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我才高一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有整整三年的考虑时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样都无法得出结论的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学考试！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想学习！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  就算气馁也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为考虑我想成为的东西才苦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就应该试着先去考虑自己想做什么不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}体！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砰砰砰的吵死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为现在几点了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那么难懂的事情我不清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之开始做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做作业！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伞蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用折纸来做是相当麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做出我大概至少得要废掉两张折纸吧
