Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:22.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}现在才第一次发觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:27.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小时满脑子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:29.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意识不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}觉得与平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:30.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:33.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N情\N相\N悦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  视线和他对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:44.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么什么  这种忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:55.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那种事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感觉都要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急转直下的我的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:06.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼间  脸像着火般变得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:09.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎么可能  我的手居然在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是所谓的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  说话咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我语无伦次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:20.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你对我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:18.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N对\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:29.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
